article_metadata.description: Tennis star Andy Murray married his longtime girlfriend Kim Sears on Saturday, People reports.The couple tied the knot in Dunblane, Scotland, Murray's hometown. Murray, 27 wore a formal kilt to the event, while his bride, 27, opted for a white gown and veil.Where every Game of Thrones character left offThe Olympic gold medalist and Wimbledon winner began dating Sears in 2005 and got engaged this past November.
